HDD MOUNT----

create a hdd folder in standrad user

1. Mkdir Hdd

2. vi /etc/fstab
3. /dev/sda1 <tab> /home/users/user-name/hdd <tab> ext4 <tab> defaults <tab> 0 0	
3. mount -a






